<div id="main-container">

<h2>Having Trouble? Let's do something about that.</h2>

    <div class="faq-header">Frequently Asked Questions</div>

    <div class="faq-content">
        <div class="faq-question">
            <input id="q1" type="checkbox" class="panel">
            <div class="plus">+</div>
            <label for="q1" class="panel-title">What is the return policy?</label>
            <div class="panel-content">For each order it is 45 days from the date the order was placed.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-question">
            <input id="q2" type="checkbox" class="panel">
            <div class="plus">+</div>
            <label for="q2" class="panel-title">How long does shipping take?</label>
            <div class="panel-content">Orders placed within Monday-Wednesday between 8am-5pm should arrive within the next two business days.
                Any order placed after Wednesday should be delivered by the following Monday or start of the business week. </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-question">
            <input id="q3" type="checkbox" class="panel">
            <div class="plus">+</div>
            <label for="q3" class="panel-title">What happens if I receive an incorrect or defective item?</label>
            <div class="panel-content">If you happen to get a damaged/incorrect item within your shipment. Please take a photo of the item or items and include your order number (Located in you personal profile in your orders tab)
                for validation of the order. Afterward, we shall be in contact with you about the next steps to rectify your order within the next several hours.
                Our email is (helpfaq@hikari.com).</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-question">
            <input id="q4" type="checkbox" class="panel">
            <div class="plus">+</div>
            <label for="q4" class="panel-title"> What if I have an error with the order that hasn't shipped yet?</label>
            <div class="panel-content"> Please  email us with the order number to create a ticket for your situation. (helpfaq@hikari.com)</div>
        </div>


    <div class="faq-question">
        <input id="q5" type="checkbox" class="panel">
        <div class="plus">+</div>
        <label for="q5" class="panel-title"> I placed too many items inside my cart and I didn't need all of this?</label>
        <div class="panel-content"> Before you check out you will be able to remove any or all items from the cart. Please double-check all items before placing
            your order!</div>
    </div>



    <div class="faq-question">
        <input id="q6" type="checkbox" class="panel">
        <div class="plus">+</div>
        <label for="q6" class="panel-title"> Our Promise </label>
        <div class="panel-content"> Here at AutoPlace we strive to not only provide the best service when buying our products. We also strive to only supply you products from highly
            reputable manufactures that stand up to match dealer OEM quality. You won't have to worry about if it fit your vehicle due to our personal standards that each part must meet to be on
            our shelves.</div>
    </div>



<div class="faq-question">
    <input id="q7" type="checkbox" class="panel">
    <div class="plus">+</div>
<label for="q7" class="panel-title"> What if I can't find what I'm looking for?</label>
<div class="panel-content"> Please  take a look at the top right hand corner of our website to find our search bar. This will
    allow you to search for the item you are looking for throughout the website no matter what part of the website you are on.  </div>
</div>

